# **/dist/
# **/tmp/
# **/out-tsc/
# **/bazel-out/

# --- Frontend / Angular (im Unterordner frontend/) ---
**/frontend/dist/
**/frontend/tmp/
**/frontend/out-tsc/
**/frontend/bazel-out/
**/frontend/.angular/
**/frontend/.sass-cache/

# --- Node Modules ---
# Sucht 'node_modules' überall im Projekt
# **/node_modules/
node_modules/

# --- Node / npm (sucht in allen Unterordnern) ---
**/node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# --- Backend (Django) ---
