# backend/env/
# backend/db.sqlite3
# **/__pycache__/
# *.py[cod]
# *.env
*Soloproject KanMind.md

# --- Backend / Django (im Unterordner backend/) ---
**/backend/__pycache__/
**/backend/*.py[cod]
**/backend/db.sqlite3
**/backend/db.sqlite3-journal
**/backend/local_settings.py

# Virtuelle Umgebungen (Python)
**/backend/env/
**/backend/.venv/
**/backend/venv/
**/backend/ENV/

